==English==

===Alternative spellings===
*[[tumourigenesis]] (British English)

===Etymology===
From [[tumor]] + -i- + suffix -genesis, indicating origination, emergence, formation, beginning

===Noun===
{{en-noun|-}}

# Production of a new [[tumor]] or tumors.
# The process involved in the production of a new tumor or tumors.

